(399, 4, 44, 1, 'Water Lily', 'Water-Lily', 'Water-Lili.jpg', 'Water-Lili.jpg', 'Water-Lili.jpg', 'Water-Lili.jpg,Water-Lilie1.jpg,Water-Lilie2.jpg,Water-Lilie3.jpg,Water-Lilies5.jpg,Water-Lilies6.jpg,Water-Lilies7.jpg,Water-Lilies8.jpg,Water-Lilies9.jpg', '<p><br />In Bangladesh&nbsp;Water Lilies&nbsp;are more found during the rainy season. Water Lilies are aquatic perennials beautiful flower. A&nbsp;Water Lily&nbsp;is a great plant for the center of a pond. It scientific name is&nbsp;<strong><em><u>Nymphaea</u></em></strong><strong> <em><u>odorata</u></em></strong><em><u>.</u></em> There are about 40 species of water lilies in the world, plus numerous hybrids and varieties. This water plant can be grown in ponds or basins/containers which can hold 4 to 5 liters of water.&nbsp;These can be seen in &nbsp;different colors such as White, Violet, Pink.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>', 'WL001', 342, '2012-05-24 10:02:33', 1, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(400, 4, 44, 1, 'Kadam Flower', 'Kadam-Flower', 'Kadam-Ful.jpg', 'Kadam-Ful.jpg', 'Kadam-Ful.jpg', 'Kadam-Ful-3.jpg,Kadam-Ful.jpg,Kadam-Flower-5.jpg,Kadam-Ful-1.jpg,Kadam-Ful-2.jpg', '<p><br /><strong>Kadam Flower</strong> is a rainy season flower. It blooms in each branches of the tree. Scientific name is <em><u>Neolamarckia</u></em> <em><u>cadamba,</u></em> commonly called Kadam (Bengali: ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â®/ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â®ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â§ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚ÂÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬). Kadam flower is an evergreen flower and grows in South andSoutheast Asia.<br /><br /><br />&nbsp;</p>', 'KF002', 412, '2012-05-24 10:06:27', 2, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(401, 4, 44, 1, 'Krishnachura Flower', 'Krishnachura-Flower', 'KRISHNACHURA-6.jpg', 'KRISHNACHURA-6.jpg', 'KRISHNACHURA-6.jpg', 'Yellow-poinciana-full bloom.jpg,Flamboyant-2.jpg,Flowers_delhi.jpg,KRISHNACHURA-6.jpg,KRISHNOCHURA.jpg,Royal_Poinciana-1.jpg,Royal_Poinciana-2.jpg', '<p><br />Scientific name is <strong><em><u>Delonix</u></em></strong> <strong><em><u>regia</u></em></strong>&nbsp;. Krishnachura is rainy season flower. It blooms when rains in continuously. After ending the rain it looks like a Flower of Fire Tree. Most of the people of&nbsp; Bangladesh is called &ldquo;Krishnachura &ldquo; and the English names for krishnachura are given in the book are : Fire Tree, Flame Tree, Gold Mohr, Gold Mohur, Gul Mohur, Royal Gul Mohur, Royal Peacock Flower.<br />&nbsp;</p>', 'KF003', 150, '2012-05-24 10:10:15', 3, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(402, 4, 44, 1, 'Orchid Flower', 'Orchid-Flower', 'Thailand-Orchid.jpg', 'Thailand-Orchid.jpg', 'Thailand-Orchid.jpg', 'Thailand-Orchid.jpg,ascocentrum_ampulaceum.jpg,bamboo_orchid.jpg,beallara_purplepassion.jpg,dorisia_sunset.jpg,Orchid-1.jpg,Orchid-2.jpg,Orchid-Flower-3.jpg', '<p><br />There are about 25,000 to 30,000 known species of orchids around the world. Orchids are found in all continents except Antarctica, from hot tropical jungles to the cold climate inNorth America. However, some orchids are&nbsp; found only in certain region of the world and nowhere else, for example, the Vanda genus colonizes onlySouth East Asia. Orchids are often seen in flower arrangements because there are so many different types and they add color to any bouquet.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>', 'OF004', 780, '2012-05-24 10:12:51', 4, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(403, 4, 44, 1, 'Aparajita( Indigo flower)', 'Aparajita-Indigo-flower-', 'Aparajita-3.jpg', 'Aparajita-3.jpg', 'Aparajita-3.jpg', 'Aparajita-1.jpg,Aparajita-2.jpg,Aparajita-3.jpg,Aparajita-4.jpg,Aparajita-5.jpg,Aparajita-6.jpg,Aparajita-7.jpg,Aparajita-8.jpg', '<span><br />These&nbsp;flowers&nbsp;bloom plentifully in rainy season and have<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>attractive,&nbsp;beautiful stems and flowers on these stems are star-shaped. Main color is vavy blue and other colors are seen such as violet,&nbsp;white and off-white. Main reason of their popularity is their attractive and deep&nbsp;colors.&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;</span>', 'AP005', 490, '2012-05-24 10:23:57', 5, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(404, 4, 45, 1, 'Snapdragon Flower', 'Snapdragon-Flower', 'Snapdragon_flower-3.jpg', 'Snapdragon_flower-3.jpg', 'Snapdragon_flower-3.jpg', 'Snapdragon_flower-3.jpg,snapdragon-flowers-assorted.jpg,define-snapdragon-4.jpg,Snapdragon_flower-1.jpg,Snapdragon_flower-2.jpg', '<p><strong><br />Snapdragons</strong> bloom plentifully in summer season and have attractive and refreshing colors like purple, red, yellow and white.<em><strong> </strong></em><strong>Snapdragon</strong>&nbsp;is an annual flower that children love because they can snap open the flowers like puppets. Snapdragons endure cool weather . In many occasions these flowers are used &nbsp;to use &nbsp;flower arrangements and are sold as&nbsp;bouquets in the markets.<br /> <br /> <strong>Scientific name:</strong>&nbsp;<em><u>Antirrhinum</u></em>&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><u>majus<br /><br /></u></em></p>', 'SF001', 890, '2012-05-24 10:31:07', 1, '194,401', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(405, 4, 45, 1, 'Dahlia Flower', 'Dahlia-Flower', 'Pink_Dahlia.jpg', 'Pink_Dahlia.jpg', 'Pink_Dahlia.jpg', 'flower-pink-dahlia.jpg,Pink_Dahlia.jpg,Dahlia.jpg,dahlia-flower-cerise.jpg', '<p><strong><br />Dahlias</strong> are classified according to flower shape and arrangement of petals. They have a wide height range (1 to 6 ft) and a variety of flower shapes and sizes (2 to 12 inches). Color range includes orange, pink, purple, red, scarlet, yellow, and white.&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;<em><strong></strong></em></p>', 'DF002', 190, '2012-05-24 10:33:36', 2, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(406, 4, 45, 1, 'Gladiolus Flower', 'Gladiolus-Flower', 'gladiolus-flower_24.jpg', 'gladiolus-flower_24.jpg', 'gladiolus-flower_24.jpg', 'gladiolus-pic.jpg,pinkflowersgladiolus.jpg,gladioli-euphorbia.jpg,gladiolus-1.jpg,gladiolus.jpg,Gladiolus-Espresso.jpg,gladiolus-flower-5.jpg,gladiolus-flower_24.jpg', '<p><span><br />These&nbsp;flowers&nbsp;bloom plentifully in&nbsp;summer&nbsp;season and have<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>attractive,&nbsp;beautiful stems and flowers on these stems are star-shaped. They come in varieties of colors including red, green, yellow and blue. Main reason of their popularity is their attractive and elegant colors. These flowers not only add beauty to your garden but are also used in making bouquets and floral arrangements.&nbsp;Its market demands quite well.<br /><br />&nbsp;</span><strong></strong></p>', 'GF003', 560, '2012-05-24 10:37:35', 3, '187', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(407, 4, 45, 1, 'Cone Flower', 'Cone-Flower', 'Cone-Flower-8.jpg', 'Cone-Flower-8.jpg', 'Cone-Flower-8.jpg', 'Cone-Flower-1.jpg,Cone-Flower-2.jpg,Cone-Flower-3.jpg,Cone-Flower-4.jpg,Cone-Flower-5.jpg,Cone-Flower-6.jpg,Cone-Flower-7.jpg,Cone-Flower-8.jpg', '<br />These flowers can grow up to 3&rsquo; tall so they can be planted at the back of other flowers especially if flower beds are circular, oval or in the shape of kidney. They like full sun for their growth and bloom from mid-summer into fall<br /><br />&nbsp;', 'CF004', 455, '2012-05-24 10:43:32', 4, '406', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(408, 4, 45, 1, 'Cosmos Flower', 'Cosmos-Flower', 'cosmos_wallpaper-3.jpg', 'cosmos_wallpaper-3.jpg', 'cosmos_wallpaper-3.jpg', 'cosmos-2.jpg,Cosmos-3.jpg,cosmos_chocolate.jpg,cosmos_flower_yellow1.jpg,Cosmos_large.jpg,cosmos_sulphureus.jpg,cosmos_wallpaper-3.jpg,cosmos-pink.jpg,Cosmos-White.jpg', '<br /><strong>Cosmos</strong> are herbaceous perennial plants growing 0.3&ndash;2 m tall. The leaves are simple, pinnate, or bipinnate, and arranged in opposite pairs. Different types of colors are seen &nbsp;yellow, red,chocolate , orange, white-pink, pink and purple etc.It increase the beauty of the garden and home yard.<br /><br /><br /><br />&nbsp;', 'CF005', 478, '2012-05-24 10:51:57', 5, '407', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(409, 4, 46, 1, 'Apple Blossom (Pyrus coronaria)', 'Apple-Blossom-Pyrus-coronaria-', 'pyrus_coronaria.jpg', 'pyrus_coronaria.jpg', 'pyrus_coronaria.jpg', 'apple_blossom_white.jpg,apple_blossomPyrus_Malus_coronaria.jpg,flamin_fury.jpg,michigan-state-flower-apple-blossom.jpg,michigan-state-tree-eastern-white-pine.jpg,pyrus_coronaria.jpg', '<strong><br />Apple blossom (Pyrus coronaria)</strong> is Arkansas State Flower. Apple blossom is one of the most fragrant and beautiful flowered species. Apple blossom tree is a good sized tree, with white, pink tinted flowers followed by round, glossy, bright green fruits. Pyrus coronaria are marvelous flowers for every spring season. These aromatic blooms are the official state flowers of two American states that are Arkansas and Michigan<br /><br />&nbsp;', 'AB001', 255, '2012-05-24 11:00:15', 1, '404,191', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(410, 4, 46, 1, 'Freesia Flower', 'Freesia-Flower', 'red_freesia-flower.jpg', 'red_freesia-flower.jpg', 'red_freesia-flower.jpg', 'freesia-flower-2.jpg,freesia-flower-3.jpg,freesia-flower-4.jpg,freesia-flower-hybride.jpg,freesia-yellow.jpg,Hot-Pink-Freesia-Fucsia-Flower.jpg,red_freesia-flower.jpg', '<p><strong><br />Freesia</strong> is&nbsp; wedding flowers. Freesia flowers are a sweetly fragrant popular accent flower. Fresh bulk freesia is available year round in a variety of bright beautiful petal colors.&nbsp; Every year more than110 million flowers are sold in theUnited Kingdom. This plant is one of the most famous one for the majority of people. It is available in white, yellow, lavender, mauve, orange, gold, pink, red, velvet shades and colors.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>', 'FF002', 350, '2012-05-24 11:03:27', 2, '406,401', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(411, 4, 46, 1, 'Begonia Flower', 'Begonia-Flower', 'begonia-flower-2.jpg', 'begonia-flower-2.jpg', 'begonia-flower-2.jpg', 'Begonia-3.jpg,Begonia.jpg,begonia_0489.jpg,begonia_angel_wing3_s.JPG,begonia-flower-2.jpg,begonia-flower-display.jpg,begonia-green-rose.jpg,begonia-red.jpg', '<p><br />Mainly begonia plants are grown and cultivated due to its asymmetrical leaves and bright colorful blooms. The flowers look showy and large. Its blossoms are available in such colors as white, pink, red, orange and yellow. It counts mote than 900 species inhabiting in such tropical climates as Central and South America, southern Asia andAfrica.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>', 'BF003', 470, '2012-05-24 11:07:52', 3, '410,406', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(412, 4, 46, 1, 'Calla Lily Flower', 'Calla-Lily-Flower', 'calla_lilly_wedding_flower_picture.jpg', 'calla_lilly_wedding_flower_picture.jpg', 'calla_lilly_wedding_flower_picture.jpg', 'calla_lilly_flower.jpg,calla_lilly_wedding_flower_picture.jpg,calla_lily.jpg,calla_lily_1.jpg,calla_lily_bunch.jpg,Calla-Lily-Flower-Assorted.jpg,callalilyflowerswhite.jpg,calla-wedding-bouquet-3.jpg', '<br />The blossoms are available during the whole year in various shades of red, mauve-pink, ivory and golden-yellow. The cut flower may stay for 4-8 days. It does well at room temperature and requires much water. Calla lily is commonly used in contemporary designs and various floral arrangements for wedding occasions, corsages, and boutonnieres.<br /><br />&nbsp;', 'CL004', 367, '2012-05-24 11:12:28', 4, '399', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(413, 4, 46, 1, 'Bloodroot', 'Bloodroot', 'bloodroot-4.jpg', 'bloodroot-4.jpg', 'bloodroot-4.jpg', 'bloodroot-4.jpg,Bloodroot.jpg,bloodroots-4.jpg,bloodroot-sanguinaria.jpg,Bloodroot-White-1.jpg,Bloodroot-White-2.jpg,Bloodroot-yellow.jpg', '<p><em><strong><br />Bloodroot</strong></em>&nbsp;is a beautiful&nbsp;<em>flower</em>&nbsp;with roots that produce a red dye.&nbsp;Bloodroot is a beautiful wildflower of the Eastern woodlands that is fast becoming a popular flower for shade gardens. Its curious name comes from its blood-red sap, which was once used as a dye by Native Americans. The blooming time is March, April and May. This flowering plant has common names as Bloodwort, Coon Root, Snakebite, Sweet Slumber, Indian Plant or Red Puccoon Root.<br /><br />Life Cycle: Perennial&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Scientific Name: <em><u>Sanguinaria</u></em><em> <u>canadensis<br /><br /><br /></u></em></p>', 'BD005', 460, '2012-05-24 11:17:19', 5, '409,192', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(414, 4, 47, 1, 'Acacia Flower', 'Acacia-Flower', 'Acacia Flower.jpg', 'Acacia Flower.jpg', 'Acacia-Flower.jpg', 'acacia_dealbata_mimosa_tree_flowers.jpg,acacia_farnesiana_flowers_big.jpg,Acacia_flowers.jpg,Acacia-dealbatasm.jpg,acacia-tree-flower.jpg,white-acacia-flowers.jpg,Acacia-Flower.jpg,Acacia-Flower-3.jpg', '<p><br /><strong>Acacia</strong> plants are shrubs and trees that are typically thorny and bear pods.ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â AcaciaÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â is well-represented in southernCaliforniaparks and gardens with dozens of different species. It is a small deciduous acacia tree known by the common names Rfaudraksha, Gum Acacia, Gum Arabic Tree, or Gum Senegal Tree. Acacias are commonly cultivated throughout temperate, tropical and desert regions, and include numerous distinctive growth forms with a profusion of yellow or white flower clusters.ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â It provides us hardwoodsÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â .<br /><br />ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â </p>', 'AF001', 378, '2012-05-24 11:24:26', 6, '406,404', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(415, 4, 40, 1, 'Suit', 'Suit', 'db_suit.jpg', 'db_suit.jpg', 'db_suit.jpg', 'Black-Solid-Slim-Fit-Suit.jpg,db_suit.jpg,style_suit.jpg,suit-1.jpg,suit.jpg,suit_ferraro.jpg,suit_umbria.jpg', '<br />A&nbsp;<strong>suit</strong>&nbsp;is a style of shirt which is wore over the shirts. Suits&nbsp;are typically made of&nbsp;synthetic cloths. A synthetic made suit looks more attractive and glorious. Men can be used suit as party or official dress. Branded suits are more better quality.<strong> </strong>Suits are<strong> </strong>available in different shapes, sizes and color combinations in the markets.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;', 'ST01', 2000, '2012-05-24 12:22:46', 1, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(416, 4, 40, 1, 'Men''s Shirt', 'Men''s-Shirt', 'Stripe-Shirt.jpg', 'Stripe-Shirt.jpg', 'Stripe-Shirt.jpg', 'Color-Shirt.jpg,Formal-Shirt.jpg,formal-shirts.jpg,party-wear-shirts.jpg,Stripe-Shirt.jpg', '<p><strong><br />Men''s Shirts</strong>&nbsp;are Casual Shirts, Cotton shirts, Stripe Shirts,&nbsp;Formal shirts,&nbsp;Official Shirts and Party Wear. These shirts can be used with suits, ties or boo ties .During the hot weather men can be used pure cotton shirts or T-shirts as official or formal dress.&nbsp;These shits are available in different shapes, sizes and color combinations in the market.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>', 'MS002', 700, '2012-05-24 12:45:18', 2, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(417, 4, 40, 1, 'Men''s Pant', 'Men''s-Pant', 'High-Handcraft-Men-s-Formal-Pants.jpg', 'High-Handcraft-Men-s-Formal-Pants.jpg', 'High-Handcraft-Men-s-Formal-Pants.jpg', 'Black-Pant.jpg,Gray-Color-Pant.jpg,High-Handcraft-Men-s-Formal-Pants.jpg,Men-s-Formal-Pant.jpg,mens-formal-pants.jpg,Pant.jpg', '<p><strong>Men''s Pants</strong> are Casual Pants, Cotton Pants, Stripe Pants and Formal Pants. These Pants can be used &nbsp;with different types of shits including Plain Color Shirt, Stripe Shirts and Formal Shits. During the Winter season men can be used different types of Pants with shirts or T-shirts.&nbsp;These pants are available in different shapes, sizes and color combinations in the markets. Pure Cotton Pants are more comfortable. Can collect better quality pants from branded product shop.</p>', 'MP003', 1500, '2012-05-24 12:50:30', 3, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(418, 4, 40, 1, 'T Shirt', 'T-Shirt', 'T-Shirt-Blue.jpg', 'T-Shirt-Blue.jpg', 'T-Shirt-Blue.jpg', 'Black-T-Shirt.jpg,Different-T-Shirt.jpg,Stripe-T-shirt.jpg,T-shirt.jpg,T-Shirt-Ash-Color.jpg,T-Shirt-Blue.jpg,T-shirt-red-got-glass.jpg', '<p><span>A<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>T-shirt</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>(<strong>T shirt</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>or<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>tee</strong>) is a style of<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><span>shirt</span>. A T-shirt is button less and collarless, usually with short sleeves and frequently a round neck line. T-shirts are typically made of cotton fibers (sometimes others). T-shirts can be decorated with text and/or pictures, and they are often used to advertise , promoting products, companies, films and websites. T-shirt fashions include many styles for both men and women, and for all age groups, including baby, youth, teen, adult and elderly sizes.</span></p>', 'TS004', 570, '2012-05-24 12:56:23', 4, '416', '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(419, 4, 40, 1, 'Tie', 'Tie', 'Stripe-Tie.jpg', 'Stripe-Tie.jpg', 'Stripe-Tie.jpg', 'Bow-tie.jpg,Custom-tie.JPG,Interview-Business-Ties.jpg,Print-tie.jpg,silk-twill-bunny-printed-tie.jpg,stripe_tie.jpg,Stripe-Bow-Tie.jpg,Stripe-Tie.jpg', '<p><span><br />Men can wear different types of ties including formal ties or bow ties with their shirts. For wedding Ceremonies bow ties are most used. Formal ties are most used in office and any party and most used in winter season in each country. Ties are made of cotton fibers or others and decorated with stripe, boll print or plain color etc.<br />&nbsp;</span></p>', 'TE005', 1000, '2012-05-24 01:01:41', 5, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(420, 4, 41, 1, 'Sari', 'Sari', 'Jamdani_Saree.jpg', 'Jamdani_Saree.jpg', 'Jamdani_Saree.jpg', 'Gray-Pillar-1.jpg,Jamdani_Saree -Red-Black.jpg,Jamdani_Saree.jpg,KATAN-SILK-JAMDANI-SAREE.jpg,Pictures-of-pure-cotton-saree.jpg,plain-ivory-color-cotton-saree.jpg,SilkSareecombines.jpg', '<p>A&nbsp;<strong>sari</strong>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<strong>saree</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>is a strip of unstitched cloth, worn by females, ranging from four to nine yards in length that is draped over the body in various styles.&nbsp;It is popular inIndia, &nbsp;Bangladesh,Nepal, &nbsp;Pakistan, &nbsp;Sri Lanka, &nbsp;Bhutan,Burma, &nbsp;Malaysia &nbsp;and &nbsp;Singapore. The most common style is for the sari to be wrapped around the waist, with one end then draped over the shoulder baring the midriff. Different type of saris such as cotton, silk, tat, siphon are available in the market.</p>', 'SR001', 5000, '2012-05-24 01:07:47', 1, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(421, 4, 41, 1, 'Long Shalwar kameez', 'Long-Shalwar-kameez', 'new-pakistani-salwar-kameez.jpg', 'new-pakistani-salwar-kameez.jpg', 'new-pakistani-salwar-kameez.jpg', 'new-pakistani-salwar-kameez.jpg,new-salwar-kameez-designs.jpg,Printed-Silk-Kameez-Salwar.jpg,Summer-Salwar-Kameez-Design-.jpg', '<p><strong><br />Long Shalwar kameez</strong>&mdash;alternatively salwar kameez or shalwar qameez&mdash;is a traditional dress worn by both women and men in &nbsp;South Asia andCentralAsia. Shalwar are loose pajama-like trousers. The legs are wide at the top and narrow at the ankle. The kameez is a long shirt or tunic. The side seams (known as the chaak), left open below the waist-line, give the wearer greater freedom of movement. Different type of long shalwar kameez(Pure cotton, silk, tat, siphon) are available in the market.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>', 'LS002', 1700, '2012-05-24 01:13:35', 2, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(422, 4, 41, 1, 'Short Salwar Kameez', 'Short-Salwar-Kameez', 'Printed-Silk-Kameez-Salwar.jpg', 'Printed-Silk-Kameez-Salwar.jpg', 'Printed-Silk-Kameez-Salwar.jpg', 'Printed-Silk-Kameez-Salwar.jpg,Salwar-Kameez-Neck-Design.jpg,salwar-kameez-short.jpg,Salwar-Kameez-Wedding-Designs.jpg,Short-Salwar-Kameez.jpg', '<p><span><br />These days a number of ladies can be seen in different cloths like pant (salwar) upto knee and short kameez upto hips but they use the terminology as salwar kameez. As the modern time changed the life of human beings, the ladies salwar kameez changed their trends. Normally in the traditional salwar kameez, the kameez is long upto knee. Gradually the size of kameez became less upto hips with parallel and bootcut pants. The short kameez are very famous with buttons and embroidery at the front.<br /><br />&nbsp;</span></p>', 'SS003', 2000, '2012-05-24 01:19:01', 3, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(423, 4, 41, 1, 'Kurta', 'Kurta', 'Sky-Color-Kurta.jpg', 'Sky-Color-Kurta.jpg', 'Sky-Color-Kurta.jpg', 'LADIES_KURTA.jpg,LADIES_KURTA_GRAY_COLOR.jpg,LADIES_KURTA_TRIPE.jpg,Ladies-Kurta.jpg,Printed-Kurta.jpg,Sky-Color-Kurta.jpg', '<strong>kurta</strong>&nbsp;is a traditional item of clothing worn in Afghanistan, Pakistan, Nepal, India, Bangladesh, and Sri Lanka. Kurta pajama is one of the basic ethnic clothing of men especially in South Asia. It is considered one of the most comfortable wear of ethnic fashion that is a must to portray the manly charm in a sophisticated way in any traditional event or semi-formal occasions. Kurta Pajama, consists of two pieces of garments, one is kurta and the other is pajama. Basically kurta is more like a long shirt like loose fitting outfit that reaches up to or below knees, whereas the second one, i.e. pajama or pyjama, is a lightweight drawstring trouser.', 'KT004', 700, '2012-05-26 09:10:46', 4, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(424, 4, 41, 1, 'Ladies Shirts', 'Ladies-Shirts', 'women-shirts-red.jpg', 'women-shirts-red.jpg', 'women-shirts-red.jpg', 'women_light_yellow_shirt.jpg,women-shirts-red.jpg,Women-shirts-red-color.jpg,women-s-shirt-with-black-colar.jpg,women-s-t-shirts-black.jpg', '<strong>Ladies Shirts</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>represent the ultimate in shirting elegance. Women&nbsp;shirt fashions include many styles for both young girls and women, and for all age groups, including baby, youth, teen, adult and elderly sizes. At present like men&rsquo;s shirts fashions different type of women shirts such as T-shirt, short shirts, high neck shits and neck less T-shirts are &nbsp;more available in the market places. Women shirts might be cotton or synthetic cloths. Branded shirts are more comfortable.', 'LS005', 1200, '2012-05-26 09:16:40', 5, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(425, 4, 42, 1, 'Party Dress', 'Party-Dress', 'Pretty-Kids-Party-Dresses.jpg', 'Pretty-Kids-Party-Dresses.jpg', 'Pretty-Kids-Party-Dresses.jpg', 'Baby-Cotton-Dress.jpg,Baby-Swanky-Dress.jpg,child-fancy-dress-party-clothes.jpg,girls-dress.jpg,pink-dress.jpg,Pretty-Kids-Party-Dresses.jpg', 'We sees different types of baby dresses such as &nbsp;Communion dresses, Christening dresses, Party dresses, Fancy party dresses and Empire dresses. Party and Fancy dresses are typically made of synthetic clothes. Cotton dresses are more better for baby. But&nbsp; occasionally they can wear Party and Fancy dresses.', 'PD001', 2500, '2012-05-26 09:26:01', 1, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(426, 4, 42, 1, 'Summer Dress', 'Summer-Dress', 'shirtt-adress.jpg', 'shirtt-adress.jpg', 'shirtt-adress.jpg', 'Bady-Dress.jpg,BirthdayCoutureDress.jpg,Empire-Dress.jpg,Girls-Shortsleeve-Dress.jpg,Kid-adress.jpg,kids-party-dresses.jpg,shirtt-adress.jpg,Skirt.jpg', '<strong><br />Summer</strong> is the season of&nbsp; hot winds and temperatures. During the summer the temperature rises very high that&rsquo;s why every mother should over take cake to their babies. They should always use cotton made dresses for their baby. Cotton made dresses are more comfortable.<br /><br />', 'SD002', 1500, '2012-05-26 09:30:07', 2, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
(427, 4, 42, 1, 'Winter Dress', 'Winter-Dress', 'Winter-Dress.jpg', 'Winter-Dress.jpg', 'Winter-Dress.jpg', 'babygap_dress.jpg,classic-baby-winter-holiday-coat.jpg,Minnie-Mouse-design-kids-clothing.jpg,Wilnter-Dress.jpg,Winter-Dress.jpg', '<p><strong><br />Winter</strong> is the season of strong winds and cold temperatures. Put an outfit on the baby which envelops him from the head to toe. Choose clothing that has a cap or hood with a covering for the ears to keep the infant''s head, ears and neck extra warm. Every mother can store a thick shirt, thermal pant, baby jackets, warms socks, gloves and&nbsp; hats before coming the winter. In winter every mother should be more sincere toward&nbsp; her baby.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>', 'WD003', 800, '2012-05-26 09:33:51', 3, NULL, '0', '1', '', '', ''),
